		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hi all,
<br />
<br />I can't find any info on how to make a flashable cartridge. I would like something like a normal cartridge but with which I could plug an USB cable (parallel maybe ?) and read or write the rom.
<br />
<br />I just want that to use my developments on my real NES...

		

